attachments.title: CNN Reports Reading Wikileaks is Illegal, You Must Get Your Information From CNN
attachments.text: CNN tells viewers it is illegal to read the Wikileaks emails so they must only learn about them through the lens of the media. According to CNN, Hillary Clinton’s basement server full of classified material is OK. But average Americans reading Wikileaks are a major crime. Chris Cuomo at CNN is the worst sort of […]
